{"tid":889602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"喜歡上一個朋友 成功率是0","createTime":"2018-11-04T16:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T19:42:10.000Z","uid":220520,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8be6747c9050d60a43e88ac216ba3967b001b5ea","tid":889602,"uid":220520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"認識了數年<br />\n很多低潮 都有你陪我走過<br />\n一同踏過很多路 做過很多事<br />\n有很多回憶<br />\n<br />\n一直 你在外面交友<br />\n我都不想 但不知道如何阻止你<br />\n那些人一個又一個離開你 總會盼望你會停止<br />\n然而 你卻只會重覓另一個 <br />\n我 只能站在你身邊看著你<br />\n<br />\n這次 他對你很上心<br />\n願意聽你傾訴 陪你渡過生活每分每刻<br />\n漸漸 我感覺連站的位置都沒了<br />\n也明白到 別人可以給你的 我不可以<br />\n<br />\n我開始抽身 <br />\n卻實在掩沒不到情緒<br />\n奈何 你我已猶如陌路人<br />\n沒有感情的對話 數句便終止了話題<br />\n<br />\n此刻 我已無能為力<br />\n只能祝福你 遇到對的他<br />\n要是你能幸福 我也會真心祝賀你的"},{"pid":"03e0ea39c2fd206121382a08ba4813a1f923fa41","tid":889602,"uid":220520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83105722bf0016b8fdf1f9115c517d756c71d1f6","tid":889602,"uid":220520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d5f50fec26cf9a7076565cfcd51ed05cb98889","tid":889602,"uid":133420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲"},{"pid":"08c524f0a2c0f34dc818414f75782f84a851a910","tid":889602,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T19:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6a02c72e07caaa44a6a778a12fd6e62f3214cd","tid":889602,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T19:42:10.000Z","msg":"巴打聽下最佳位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}